e</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 604, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Immovable Rod</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">One fixed point can change everything.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Fix the rod in place at any angle \u2014 it becomes an unmovable, hands-free anchor, reaching up to 5 feet.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1\u21bb</span> +5 feet of reach.</div></div></div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 605, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Smoke Bomb</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Suddenly, everyone is alone.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Fill a 10-foot area with smoke. All creatures within are <strong>Hidden</strong> from each other until the smoke clears or the <strong>Scene</strong> ends.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1\u21bb</span> Expand the area by 10 feet.</div></div></div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 606, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Weighted Net</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You can't outrun what's already around you.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Item Check</strong> \u2014 place the dice as <strong>Rooted</strong> on the target. Until <strong>Cleared</strong>, they cannot move from their position.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 607, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Decoy Doll</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">It's not lying. It's misdirection.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Trigger</div><div class=\"etxt\" style=\"font-style:italic\">You are targeted.</div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Describe how you are using the Decoy Doll to your advantage, and then choose:</div><div class=\"etxt\"><span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 2</span> to a defensive roll.</div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin:5px 0\"><div style=\"flex:1;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,#d1d5db)\"></div><span style=\"font-size:0.72em;font-weight:700;color:#9ca3af;letter-spacing:0.12em\">OR</span><div style=\"flex:1;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to left,transparent,#d1d5db)\"></div></div><div class=\"etxt\">Sacrifice the doll \u2014 the acting creature is distracted and must redirect to it.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 608, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Healer's Tincture</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The body remembers how to be whole.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Remove 2 dice of any condition from a creature you can touch.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 609, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Lantern of Revealing</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Light doesn't lie.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While lit, no creature within 30 feet can be <strong>Hidden</strong>, and illusions appear as visible overlays on reality.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 610, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Blinding Flash Powder</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You won't see this coming.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Trigger</div><div class=\"etxt\" style=\"font-style:italic\">A creature attacks you at close range.</div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Item Check</strong> \u2014 place the dice as <strong>Exposed</strong> on the attacker. Until <strong>Cleared</strong>, they are <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 611, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Rope of Climbing</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">What seems impossible from below is just a matter of the first hold.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Direct the rope to any reachable surface \u2014 it anchors there. Automatically succeed on any climbing check while using it.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 612, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Iron Spike</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Simple. Reliable. The door does not open.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Drive the spike into any door, gate, or container. It cannot be opened from the other side until removed.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 613, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Oil Flask</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The floor becomes the problem.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Coat a 10-foot area of ground. Any creature moving through must succeed on a check or become <strong>Exposed 1</strong>. If lit, any creature that acts within it takes a consequence.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 614, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Disguise Kit</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Faces are just another thing to wear.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Item Check</strong> \u2014 place the dice as <strong>Disguised</strong> on yourself. You appear as a type of NPC the GM approves. Until <strong>Cleared</strong>, you are <strong>Disguised</strong>.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 615, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Signal Whistle</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Three sharp notes. They know.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Trigger</div><div class=\"etxt\" style=\"font-style:italic\">Any time.</div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">A designated ally immediately takes one free <strong>Action</strong>. Discard after use.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 616, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Vial of Acid</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">It doesn't negotiate.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect \u2014 Choose One</div><div class=\"etxt\">Dissolve any non-magical lock, bar, or thin barrier. \u2014 or \u2014 Perform an <strong>Item Check</strong> \u2014 place the dice as <strong>Exposed</strong> on a target.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 617, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Sending Stone</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Distance is just a number. Words aren't.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Speak up to 25 words \u2014 the holder of the paired stone hears them, regardless of distance.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 618, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Caltrops</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You can't advance on ground that fights back.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Scatter in a 10-foot area. Any creature moving through becomes <strong>Rooted 1</strong> and cannot continue moving that <strong>Action</strong>.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 619, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Grappling Hook</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The ground is optional.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Attach to any surface within 30 feet \u2014 you swing to it immediately, bypassing all ground obstacles.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 620, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Blood Moss Poultice</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">It works while you sleep.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Apply to a creature. On their next <strong>Rest</strong>, they reroll their three lowest <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span>.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 621, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-any\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Lock Pick Set</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Every lock has an answer. You just have to ask politely.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Any non-magical lock opens.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Do it silently \u2014 no one notices.</div><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Keep the set in hand this <strong>Scene</strong> \u2014 it is not consumed.</div></div></div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Any</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 622, "HTML": "<div class=\"card paladin acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Bulwark</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">Your armor is not equipment. It is a promise.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Always Active</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Your armor and shield are always present \u2014 no equip action required.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Resolve Bonus</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Add +2 directly to every <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> roll you make.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 623, "HTML": "<div class=\"card fighter acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Chosen Arms</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You know these weapons. They know you.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Character Creation</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Choose 3 <span class=\"ix ix-fighter\">Fighter</span> Weapon cards \u2014 your personal arsenal, set aside outside your deck.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Weapon Slot \u2014 Session or Scene Start</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Equip one of your 3 Chosen Arms into your Weapon Slot \u2014 a unique zone separate from your hand. Only one may be equipped at a time.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Activate</div><div class=\"effect-text\">When you use the equipped weapon\u2019s effect: discard it from the slot, then <strong>Draw</strong> 1.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 629, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Bag of Tricks</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The trick isn't having the right tool. It's having three backups.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Character Creation</div><div class=\"etxt\">Draft 2 additional <strong>Item</strong> cards. These form your Bag of Tricks.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Session Start</div><div class=\"etxt\">You may place 1 of your Bag of Tricks <strong>Items</strong> in your <strong>Active Area</strong> \u2014 it is always in your hand this session.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Once per Scene</div><div class=\"etxt\"><strong>Discard</strong> 1 <strong>Item</strong> card \u2192 <strong>Draw</strong> 2.</div><div class=\"spacer\"></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 630, "HTML": "<div class=\"card connection acc-connection\" style=\"background:#f7f0e0;border-radius:8px;border:1.5px solid #c8a96e;\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Connection</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name hdr-blankname\"><span style=\"opacity:.18;font-style:italic;font-weight:600;font-size:7px\">name</span></div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Find a moment in this scene to connect with this character. Choose one:</div><ul style=\"margin:2px 0 0;padding:0 0 0 12px;list-style:disc;font-size:10.45px;line-height:1.6;color:#1c1408;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom:2px;\"><strong>Share</strong> a memory between you that feels like this moment.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:2px;\"><strong>Ask</strong> them a question that only this scene could prompt.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:2px;\"><strong>Challenge them</strong> \u2014 push them to grow or change in a way this scene requires.</li></ul><div class=\"etxt\" style=\"margin-top:4px;font-size:9.9px;\">Then, each player chooses: gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>, reclaim a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span>, or <strong>Draw 1</strong>.</div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;margin:4px 0;\"><div style=\"flex:1;height:1px;background:#c8a96e;opac